::Inu::
Inu digging his claws into Koj chest and throws at the docking bay wall.
"Your tech is sloppy today you lack focus! Your fighting like a wimp get 
some guts or are just so damn sorry you can't fight back go pity yourself 
some where else!" Whipers "I can see why SoundWave defeated you that day."

::Koj::
Koj flies hitting the wall passing right in the room next to docking bay 9. 
Koj getting a little pissed. As he skids on the ground stopping!
Koj stands fires off his thrusters flies through the hole in the wall and 
swings wildly at Inu-Yasha.

::Inu::
Inu getting hit hard rolls back. Starts spin the tip of his tail into a 
drill starts thrusting it at Koj.

::Koj::
Koj starts parrying the tail blows.

::Inu::
Inu Spins using the tail trying to knock off his feet Koj

::Koj::
Koj hits the ground hard.

::Inu::
Inu stomps Koj a few times and jumps up trying to crush him.

::Koj::
Koj rolls out of the way stands up and resets.

::Inu::
Inu lands with a thud crushing and marring the floor as Inu turns and opens 
his lancer ports and fires 8 at Koj.

::Koj::
Koj takes off running up the wall as the 8 lancers hit the wall. Koj springs 
off trying to kick Inu in the face.

::Inu::
Inu staggers spits out a little blood."Feh!" Inu jabs his claws at Koj.

::Koj::
Koj slides to the right grabs the claw and shoves it into the wall.
Koj takes this time and attacks releasing a fury of punches and kicks.

::Inu::
Inu thinks ten minutes ago he could even stand up to weak attacks now he 
fighting likes a warrior. Inu takes the blows as they start wearing on his 
chest plate damaging it.Inu uses his other claw to slash at Koj.

::Koj::
Koj getting hit by the swipe flies over to the side and quickly resets.
Koj rushes releasing a smoke bomb.

::Inu::
Inu starts using wings to clear the smoke shoots snort out a fireball at the 
Fire alarm causing water to rain in. "You can't hide Koj!"
